channel.title: Oops I Broke My Spork
channel.description: Life sucks and I KNOW IT, gain insight from people who are barely adults as we navigate life and overcome life’s challenges. All while we remain seemingly hopeful and hopeless @ the same time.

item.title: Home Not So Sweet Home (pt. 1)
item.description: Kicking off the relationship series with a talk about a semi-current living situation. Hear the thoughts from 2 roomies and the great cleaning debate. Listen closely to pick up on both areas of the discussions where maturity was present and where maturity was lacking - and where improvement needs to occur!! Tune in for a later episode on tips and tricks to diffuse and deal with unideal roommate situations.
